export const ManageThemes = ({ theme }) => {
    return (    <React.Fragment>
        <SimpleText {...TabSectionHeaderProps(theme)}>
          Help Center
        </SimpleText>
        <Grid numCols={16} numRows={9} rowUnit="28px" colUnit="28px" key={0}>
          <GridElement
            position={{
              startCol: 1,
              endCol: 17,
              startRow: 1,
              endRow: 10,
            }}
            customStyles={customStyles}
          >
            { ReactPlayer.canPlay(vidUrl) ? 
              <ReactPlayer 
              url={vidUrl}
              controls
              width="100%"
              height="100%"
              /> :
              <Unplayable theme={theme} />
            }
          </GridElement>
        </Grid>
      </React.Fragment>)
}
